<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Adolphen,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> czu <add>Berg,
                                                  grave czu </add>
<expan>Ravensb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> und
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> czu
                                                  <expan>Blanckemberg<ex>en</ex></expan></ab>
